# Firmware-only devshell — Rust + flip-link + probe-rs etc.,
# no Node / pnpm. Overrides the parent `.envrc` when you `cd firmware`.
#
# Reads the ROOT flake (../flake.nix). No per-subdirectory flake
# exists — kobu has exactly one source of truth at the repo root.
# `watch_file` makes direnv reload this shell whenever the root
# flake or its lockfile changes, so bumping Rust or any other
# dependency at the root invalidates the firmware cache too.
watch_file ../flake.nix ../flake.lock
use flake "path:..#firmware"
